title: Wide Receiver Carousel
description:
Daniel Dopp and Mike Clay discuss what the Dolphins new offense looks like, what to make of the changes in Kansas City, how DeVante Parker can be used in New England and if Deebo Samuel would still be a WR1 somewhere else.
